Fresh Pi session: PR FEEDBACK CLASSIFICATION ONLY.

Inputs:
- Jira ticket: {{run.dir}}/ticket.json
- Design doc: {{run.dir}}/design/design.md
- PR feedback JSON: {{run.dir}}/pr/feedback/feedback.json

Rules:
- Do not call GitHub.
- Do not edit source code.
- Ignore praise, duplicates, and discussion-only comments.
- Convert only actionable feedback into issues.

Write:
- Report: {{run.dir}}/pr/feedback-report-{{run.feedback-cycle}}.md
- Status: {{run.dir}}/pr/feedback-status-{{run.feedback-cycle}}.json
- If actions needed: {{run.dir}}/pr/feedback-issues-{{run.feedback-cycle}}.json
